rows.label: qev013403_MSG0006
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0007
rows.name:
I heard a big commotion.
Was that you taking out that blatta?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_JNK0010
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev013403_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Sarona the blatta is dead and she can relax.

rows.label: qev013403_JNK0020
rows.name: Caution

rows.label: qev013403_SEL0021
rows.name: Warn Sarona not to get too comfortable.

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0008
rows.name:
Whew! And wow, you really live up to the your
reputation, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0009
rows.name:
True, we're still in their territory, so anything could
happen. I sure am glad I picked a cautious partner![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0010
rows.name: So is Inisae okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0011
rows.name: Huh?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0012
rows.name:
Inisae! What's wrong?!
She...she's not moving...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0013
rows.name:
How do you do CPR on a Ma-non?! Where's the
heart located?! Can I even take a pulse?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0014
rows.name:
Aaarggh! Why didn't I bother to learn anything USEFUL
about xenos?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0015
rows.name:
Come on, wake up. ...Please? We only just became
friends. It's way too soon for good-bye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0016
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0017
rows.name: ...Friends? We are friends?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0018
rows.name: You're okay...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0019
rows.name:
You'd be my friend even though I'm a Ma-non?
Really? Really really?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_JNK0030
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev013403_SEL0031
rows.name:
Tell Inisae that she and Sarona have
been friends for a while now.

rows.label: qev013403_JNK0040
rows.name: Deny

rows.label: qev013403_SEL0041
rows.name:
Tell Inisae that she and Sarona are not
friends so much as...kindred spirits.

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0020
rows.name:
I'm so so glad. I've stared out at New LA from our ship
for some time and felt...a longing, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0021
rows.name:
I wanted to get closer to the curious cyborgs that
somehow still overflowed with warmth, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0022
rows.name:
Kindred means family, right? So our spirits are family?
What lovely lovely words you humans have![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0023
rows.name: Inisae! Are you all right?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0024
rows.name:
Ow. My joints ache, but I don't think anything is
brokenâ€”so so so that's good, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0025
rows.name:
Thank goodness! Let's get you out of this cave and
patch you up. I promise I won't let any more big,
slobbery monsters get anywhere near you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0026
rows.name: Thanks for everything, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0027
rows.name:
We gathered some great mineral samples and verified
the local wildlife. I'd say our survey's done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0028
rows.name:
Here's the reward. I was pretty useless this time around,
so you should have it all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0029
rows.name:
Yeah, I'm sure! I made a new friend from this
assignment, after all. That's more than enough
of a reward for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0030
rows.name:
We're heading out. See you back home!
...You ready, Inisae?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0031
rows.name:
Yes, Sarona. On the way down, I can point out various
mineral deposits and herbs...if you like?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013403_MSG0032
rows.name:
Hey, slow down, girl! I appreciate the thought,
but we've got to get you looked at first.[ST:wait ]
